{"lastModified":1775746052235,"uri":"c::9938368400::vessel::d5cc785a-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: \nSummer/Winter: British Virgin Islands, Costa Rica, Cuba, Florida, Leeward Islands, The Bahamas\n\nCharter Sunreef Supreme 68 Power ORCA for an exceptional yachting experience that combines performance, luxury, and innovation.\nPowered by twin IPS Volvo engines, ORCA delivers smooth, agile cruising with impressive speed. Her dynamic positioning system ensures effortless maneuverability, even in busy marinas. Life on board is both refined and practical. The expansive bow terrace invites relaxation with large sunbeds, a Jacuzzi, and a wide sun awning.\n\nThe flybridge offers two fully equipped bars, ample lounging space, and elegant dining areas for entertainment at sea. Designed to accommodate 8 guests in comfort, the yacht features a bright, custom interior with spacious 2 master suites and 2 guest double cabins, each with generous quartz-clad bathrooms. The vast main deck saloon and galley span the beam of the yacht, accented by soft grey and cream tones with bold, colorful furnishings. As the only yacht of her size in the world with a superyacht-style tender garage and expansive onboard living areas, ORCA is a true standout — a bespoke expression of sea-going sophistication.","blueprint":{"name":"ORCA","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc785a-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::a63b3510-baf4-11f0-93a1-677c90249b7e/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc785a-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::a63ede90-baf4-11f0-b6f4-49cdc0355bb9/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc785a-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::a6657960-baf4-11f0-93a2-677c90249b7e/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc785a-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::a6401710-baf4-11f0-b6f4-49cdc0355bb9/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc785a-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::a63ff00